long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Getaway Shootout Unblocked brings fast-paced, physics-based platformer action right to your Chrome browser! This extension gives you instant access to the wild multiplayer chaos, where the goal is simple—jump, shoot, and race to the getaway point before anyone else. Whether you’re on a break or need a fun distraction, this extension makes it easier than ever to jump into the action without switching tabs or visiting gaming sites.

✨ Why Install?

Instant Access: Launch the game directly from your browser—no need to search online.
Wacky Multiplayer Fun: Play solo or challenge friends locally for the ultimate showdown.
Seamless Gameplay: No downloads or sign-ups—just install and play.
Offline Support: Play anywhere, even when you’re disconnected from the internet.
Boost Your Breaks: Take a quick mental refresh during work or study sessions with fun-packed gameplay.
🔫 Ready to jump, shoot, and race to victory? Install Getaway Shootout Unblocked and escape boredom with every click! 🚀
